<p>Using the migrate framework module, how can I migrate images from drupal 6 to 7.</p>  <p>For the drupal 7 to drupal 7 migrating images, I just use the code:</p>  <pre><code>$this-&gt;addFieldMapping('field_image', 'uri_image')-&gt;separator(','); $this-&gt;addFieldMapping('field_image:destination_dir')      -&gt;defaultValue('public://'); </code></pre>  <p>It works directly because uri_image is present in the table "file_managed" in the database, but for drupal 6, images are stored in the table "file" via the "filepath" column.</p>  <p>How can make my import work, please help.</p>